00020   \brief Functions to convert from OBD output to actual values
00021   Functions declared in this file are named by their OBD Service command

00033 // http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Table_of_OBD-II_Codes
00034 
00035 /// All obd conversion functions adhere to this
00036 typedef float (*OBDConvFunc)(unsigned int A, unsigned int B,
00037     unsigned int C, unsigned int D);
00038 
00039 /// All obd reverse conversion functions adhere to this
00040 /// return value is number of values [A,B,C,D] filled.
00041 typedef int (*OBDConvRevFunc)(float val, unsigned int *A, unsigned int *B,
00042     unsigned int *C, unsigned int *D);
